data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bed 2.5 bath home in East Stroudsburg.  The home has been very well maintained since being built in 2016. The kitchen and dining area open up nicely leading to the sliding glass doors that lead out to the recently added 12x12 deck that adds a great outdoor entertainment space. Downstairs has a  powder room. The main bedroom includes large windows and a full bathroom.  Sellers are motivated will be welcoming showings beginning Saturday morning. Additional photos will be added the evening of Friday 8-18.
